Timeline¶

This document contains more or less the timeline of the project progress, open questions and notes regarding the theory and implementation.

20191023¶

I’ve cleaned up the old code (kept what can be reused) and set up the R-markdown notebook. My Skype client on the Linux machine should be working fine now, too.
